shamanapp.analyzers.general_stages.domain_name_stage module¶

class shamanapp.analyzers.general_stages.domain_name_stage.DomainNameStage(config)¶

Bases: shamanapp.analyzers.abstract_stage.AbstractStage

Detects a domain name of url. For instance, for urls http://dom.com/p1/p2, http://dom.com/p8/q1 DomainName = ‘dom.com’.

Input data:
  • url
Output data:
  • domain
Using modules:
  • urlparse (to extract a domain name)
